00:16:47,566 --> 00:16:59,891
Their children, well, if they start having the mind to take good care of their children to make them better

146
00:16:59,910 --> 00:17:05,610
You know, that will probably be a long-standing hurt in a person’s heart.

147
00:17:06,254 --> 00:17:12,179
But if they try to heal, they will heal.

148
00:17:14,148 --> 00:17:21,798
You mean only if those two who were alcoholics worked with their hearts?

149
00:17:22,192 --> 00:17:32,842
Yes, the alcoholic [parents] these days, you know how alcoholics have help here now?

150
00:17:32,861 --> 00:17:38,661
They can get better with the help of their counselors.

151
00:17:38,930 --> 00:17:50,755
And married couples, I see many who are in good marriages, and they love their children.

152
00:17:51,599 --> 00:17:59,374
